Package: oncoscopR
Type: Package
Title: Audit and Analysis Dashboard for Haematological Oncology Cohorts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hanno", "Witte", role = "aut"),
    person("Raban", "Heller", , "raban.heller@outlook.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8006-9742")))
Description: Reads tumour-documentation spreadsheets from haematological tumour
    centres and computes quality and coverage indicators, OPS-8-544 complex
    chemotherapy block counts, OPS-1-941 complex diagnostics counts,
    Kaplan-Meier analyses, oncoprint and cytogenetics summaries, plus an
    interactive Shiny dashboard for auditor live evaluation. Includes a fully
    synthetic example cohort for demonstration and testing.
